		<title>09The Mackie Academy</title>
		<content>{How have schools changed in your      
{career?}                              
  I started teaching in 1960 and the   
 emphasis then was on the three        
 'R's.The curriculum was very          
 predictable.Now schools are expected  
 to do very much more for their        
 pupils;not only to educate them       
 academically but also to prepare them 
 for leisure, employment and to provide
 the necessary pastoral care.          
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
